# One-Line Cheat Code

```text
Preorder  = Parent First
Inorder   = Parent Middle
Postorder = Parent Last
```

---

# DFS Template

```java
static void dfs(TreeNode root) {

    if(root == null)
        return;

    // Process

    dfs(root.left);

    dfs(root.right);
}
```

Only change where processing happens.

