# Interview Pattern Recognition

| Question Clue | Traversal |
|--------------|-----------|
| Root first | Preorder |
| Clone tree | Preorder |
| Serialize tree | Preorder |
| Sorted BST output | Inorder |
| Kth Smallest BST | Inorder |
| Validate BST | Inorder |
| Delete tree | Postorder |
| Height of tree | Postorder |
| Diameter of tree | Postorder |
| Bottom-up processing | Postorder |

---

# Complexity

| Traversal | Time | Space |
|------------|---------|---------|
| Preorder | O(N) | O(H) |
| Inorder | O(N) | O(H) |
| Postorder | O(N) | O(H) |

Where:

```text
N = Number of Nodes
H = Height of Tree
```

Worst Case:

```text
O(N)
```

Balanced Tree:

```text
O(log N)
```

