# Ultimate Interview Cheat Sheet

```text
PREORDER  -> Parent First
          -> Clone Tree
          -> Serialization
          -> Prefix Expression

INORDER   -> BST = Sorted Order
          -> Kth Smallest
          -> BST Validation

POSTORDER -> Children First
          -> Delete Tree
          -> Height
          -> Diameter
          -> Postfix Expression
```

